PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe US aerial bombardment continued
OL,8,Finto Monday morning, further
OL,9,Fthreatening any diplomacy to end the
OL,10,Fwar. The US and Iran are near the
OL,11,Fhalfway mark of a 60-day window to
OL,12,Fnegotiate a deal.
OL,14,FUS Central Command described its
OL,15,Fforces as hitting 140 sites, including
OL,16,Fair defence, radar and missile
OL,17,Fsystems, as well as drone capabilities
OL,18,Fand small boats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
