PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"The Strait of Hormuz is a vital
OL,8,Fmaritime corridor for global trade,"
OL,9,Fit said.
OL,11,F"Iran does not control it."
OL,13,FIranian state media reported that the
OL,14,Fstrikes killed one person in
OL,15,Fsouthwestern Iran, while four were
OL,16,Finjured.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@dO]sD@AOUsD@[O]
