PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FFollowing the overnight strikes,
OL,8,FIran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,9,FCorps said it attacked several bases
OL,10,Flinked to the US in Bahrain, Kuwait
OL,11,Fand Jordan.
OL,13,FThe escalating attacks, sparked by
OL,14,FIran striking a container ship on
OL,15,FSunday in the strait off the coast of
OL,16,FOman, again underlined that the
OL,17,Fwaterway through which 20 per cent of
OL,18,Fthe world's traded crude oil and
OL,19,Fnatural gas passes remains a key issue
OL,20,Fin negotiations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
