CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FSince the US and Israel attacked Iran
OL,8,Fon February 28, shipping through the
OL,9,Fnarrow mouth of the Persian Gulf has
OL,10,Fbeen severely disrupted.
OL,12,FIran maintained a chokehold on it by
OL,13,Fattacking commercial vessels around it
OL,14,Fand intimidating shippers.
OL,16,FAt the end of April, Brent crude
OL,17,Freached $120 a barrel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
