PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIran and US are nearly halfway through
OL,8,Fthe 60-day interim deal signed in June
OL,9,Fthat was supposed to set up talks for
OL,10,Fa permanent end to the war.
OL,12,FInstead, it has devolved into a series
OL,13,Fof attacks over the strait and its
OL,14,Ffuture, worrying world leaders that
OL,15,Fthe conflict could resume.
OL,17,FIran says it has closed the key
OL,18,Fwaterway until further notice, while
OL,19,Fthe US insists it is open.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
