OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,8,FGuard sharply rejected America's claim
OL,9,Fsaying: "The Strait of Hormuz is our
OL,10,Fterritory, and we will not allow a
OL,11,Frogue and child-killing army from the
OL,12,Fother side of the world to continue
OL,13,Fits illegal interference in it."
