OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIn a statement, United Nations
OL,8,FSecretary-General Antonio Guterres
OL,9,Fsaid: "A return to full-scale
OL,10,Fhostilities would have catastrophic
OL,11,Fconsequences."
OL,13,F"We bombed the hell out of them last
OL,14,Fnight," US President Donald Trump told
OL,15,FNBC's Meet the Press.
