OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIran retaliated by attacking nations
OL,8,Fin the region hosting US military
OL,9,Fforces, while insisting it alone must
OL,10,Fcontrol the strait and potentially
OL,11,Fcharge vessels for traveling through
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,F"The era of one-sided deals is over,"
OL,15,Fmain negotiator Mohammad Bagher
OL,16,FQalibaf, the speaker of Iran's
OL,17,Fparliament, wrote online.
OL,19,F"We told you: keep your word or pay
OL,20,Fthe price. Reality is knocking."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@eO]{D@AOU|D@`O]
