OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784038718
OL,3,CUS launches new wave of strikes
OL,4,Cagainst Iran as both vie for Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FTrump suggested last week that the
OL,8,Finterim deal in the war was "over."
OL,9,FBut mediators, including Pakistan,
OL,10,FQatar and Egypt, have continued
OL,11,Fefforts to reach a final agreement.
OL,13,FA regional official involved in
OL,14,Fmediation, speaking on condition of
OL,15,Fanonymity, said efforts to shore up
OL,16,Fthe ceasefire continued Sunday.
OL,18,FPakistan said its foreign minister
OL,19,Fspoke by phone with Iran's top
OL,20,Fdiplomat and urged "de-escalation" on
OL,21,Fboth sides.
OL,26,@pD@]OUpD@cO]|D@TOU|D@bO]
